# text = Another time, one stormy evening, when it was so dark that nothing could be distinguished, Gilliatt was near the Catiau Roque--a double row of rocks where witches, goats, and other diabolical creatures assemble and dance on Fridays--and here, it is firmly believed, that the voice of Gilliatt was heard mingling in the following terrible conversation:--
